metadata.name: Twinkle
metadata.description:
I don't know why, but I will smile.  
Because what I want is to give you a smile.  
Because when you smile, I smile too.

Life is not all about fun.  
There are difficult times and painful situations.  
On those days, I'm sure you feel sad. Sometimes you feel frustrated.  
But at any time, don't forget that.  
Remember that you can smile.

Don't give up smiling.  
When you want to smile, do it without fear.

When you smile, you are bright.  
Like a twinkle.

When I imagine you smiling like that, I feel like smiling.  
That's why I want to give you a smile.  
Because when you smile, I smile too.
